INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

USING IN DEVELOPMENT MODE

	0. Set PERL5LIB
	   export PERL5LIB=/home/user/modules/MToken/lib

	1. Initialize project
	   perl bin/mtoken -d -D foo init myfooproject

	2. Make
	   cd foo
	   perl Makefile.PL
	   make
	   make test
	   make clean

	3. Debugging
	   make clean && perl Makefile.PL && make && make clean

CREATE NEW VERSION

    * lib/MToken.pm -- in documentation (VERSION) & in code $VERSION
    * CHANGES       -- Result of command: localtime | gclip

REQUIREMENTS

    * CPAN modules:
      - LWP (perl-libwww)

